\n* `orange`\n* `gold`\n* `yellow`\n* `lime`\n* `green`\n* `cyan`\n* `blue`\n* `arcoblue`\n* `purple`\n* `pinkpurple`\n* `magenta`\n* `gray`\n\n```js\nconst { red } = getPresetColors();\n\nconsole.log(red.light);\nconsole.log(red.dark);\nconsole.log(red.primary);\n```\n\n### getRgbStr(color: string)\n\nFor a given color, get the r, g, b value in string\n\n```js\ngetRgbStr('#F53F3F') // 245,63,63\n```\n","time":{"created":"2022-01-27T13:50:52.249Z","modified":"2025-04-01T09:38:58.682Z","0.4.0":"2021-10-25T03:55:26.272Z"},"versions":{"0.4.0":{"name":"@arco-design/color","version":"0.4.0","description":"ArcoDesign color utils","main":"./src/index.js","scripts":{"test":"jest"},"keywords":["ArcoDesign","Color","utils"],"author":"","license":"MIT","dependencies":{"color":"^3.1.3"},"devDependencies":{"jest":"^26.6.3"},"gitHead":"1fbbd1905afbbd1287887f3ceab265e106b03d45","_id":"@arco-design/color@0.4.0","_nodeVersion":"14.15.4","_npmVersion":"6.14.10","dist":{"shasum":"52ddb40d318ee6df1057ca8c653cc1675023928f","size":3735,"noattachment":false,"tarball":"https://packages.aliyun.com/604c1a6bf11bae7ca07d6ad3/npm/npm-registry/@arco-design/color/-/color-0.4.0.tgz","integrity":"sha512-s7p9MSwJgHeL8DwcATaXvWT3m2SigKpxx4JA1BGPHL4gfvaQsmQfrLBDpjOJFJuJ2jG2dMt3R3P8Pm9E65q18g=="},"_npmUser":{"name":"pjy","email":"731401082@qq.com"},"directories":{},"maintainers":[{"name":"bytednpm","email":"bnpm@bytedance.com"},{"name":"n0rush","email":"michael2ib1989@gmail.com"},{"name":"yinkaihui","email":"yinkaihui0828@163.com"}],"_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"s3://npm-registry-packages","tmp":"tmp/color_0.4.0_1635134125959_0.7863392481990996"},"_hasShrinkwrap":false,"publish_time":1635134126272,"_cnpm_publish_time":1635134126272,"_cnpmcore_publish_time":"2021-12-16T18:47:10.398Z"}},"keywords":["ArcoDesign","Color","utils"],"_source_registry_name":"default"}